Im so sorry I havent played recently, Ive been so busy with School. Ive just 
read about 189 e mails so all that info is bouncing around in my head. Coyuld 
someone please tell me if TRANSANULAS and OMINOUS PRIME have been captured? I 
remember they were fighting in the Tourture chamber when MEGATRON abandoned 
them.........

~~~~~~~~~~~

::: The speeder came to a slow halt. MEGATRON looked around impatiently. 
Apparently the landscape had changed.......
    Now, as he got out of the speeder he grumbled. Rattrap followed him and 
they walked off a bit. ::::::

::: RAT TRAP ::: So, we lost or what?

::: MEGATRON, very angry ::: no...but I have misplaced my lair.

::: Ratrap laughed as Megatron scanned the vast plains for some sign of a 
settlement. :::

::: MEGATRON ::: Damn it! Damn, Damn, Damn, Damn!

::: He glanced back to the Speeder ::: Ah...wake Quickstrike, now. He is 
going to take us to his friends cave, in Asia I belive.

::: Rattrap ::: Are you sure? Thats so far away!

::: MEGATRON ::: Rat, learn to obey me and not question me! I will have my 
revenge on the Predacons and the Maximals!

::: They climbed back into the speeder and zoomed off, towrds Rowdywolfs 
cavern :::
